Pause the HSSP playback.

Pause will pause the playback, but keep the current position. A subsequent resume command will continue playback from the paused position or from the current 'live' script position/time, depending on the resume pickUp flag.

See the request body schema definition for details.

See Handy Streaming Protocol (HSP) for additional information about the HSP protocol and code samples.

Parameters
Try it out
Name	Description
X-Connection-Key *
string
(header)
minLength: 5
maxLength: 64
pattern: ^[a-zA-Z0-9]{5,64}$
Device connection key.

vUeRWzcy
